: {\n      \"login\": \"steipete\",\n      \"id\": 58493,\n      \"node_id\": \"MDQ6VXNlcjU4NDkz\",\n      \"avatar_url\": \"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/58493?v=4\",\n      \"gravatar_id\": \"\",\n      \"url\": \"https://api.github.com/users/steipete\",\n      \"html_url\": \"https://github.com/steipete\",\n      \"followers_url\": \"https://api.github.com/users/steipete/followers\",\n      \"following_url\": \"https://api.github.com/users/steipete/following{/other_user}\",\n      \"gists_url\": \"https://api.github.com/users/steipete/gists{/gist_id}\",\n      \"starred_url\": \"https://api.github.com/users/steipete/starred{/owner}{/repo}\",\n      \"subscriptions_url\": \"https://api.github.com/users/steipete/subscriptions\",\n      \"organizations_url\": \"https://api.github.com/users/steipete/orgs\",\n      \"repos_url\": \"https://api.github.com/users/steipete/repos\",\n      \"events_url\": \"https://api.github.com/users/steipete/events{/privacy}\",\n      \"received_events_url\": \"https://api.github.com/users/steipete/received_events\",\n      \"type\": \"User\",\n      \"user_view_type\": \"public\",\n      \"site_admin\": false\n    },\n    \"parents\": [\n      {\n        \"sha\": \"b24961c5d12f58a04adf9e3890a16f5de9f98126\",\n        \"url\": \"https://api.github.com/repos/openclaw/openclaw/commits/b24961c5d12f58a04adf9e3890a16f5de9f98126\",\n        \"html_url\": \"https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/commit/b24961c5d12f58a04adf9e3890a16f5de9f98126\"\n      }\n    ]\n  }\n]"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1259,"aggregated":"[\n  {\n    \"sha\": \"57949397fa181dc56fbfdb86fa1fa292bb25faea\",\n    \"node_id\": \"C_kwDOQb6kR9oAKDU3OTQ5Mzk3ZmExODFkYzU2ZmJmZGI4NmZhMWZhMjkyYmIyNWZhZWE\",\n    \"commit\": {\n      \"author\": {\n        \"name\": \"Brad Groux\",\n        \"email\": \"3053586+BradGroux@users.noreply.github.com\",\n        \"date\": \"2026-04-02T00:03:19Z\"\n      },\n      \"committer\": {\n        \"name\": \"GitHub\",\n        \"email\": \"noreply@github.com\",\n        \"date\": \"2026-04-02T00:03:19Z\"\n      },\n      \"message\": \"fix(msteams): prevent duplicate text when stream exceeds 4000 char limit (#59297)\\n\\nWhen a streamed response exceeds TEAMS_MAX_CHARS, the stream sets streamFailed=true and finalizes. Previously, hasContent returned false when streamFailed was true, causing preparePayload to pass through the full payload for block delivery, duplicating already-streamed text.\\n\\nNow tracks streamed length and strips the already-delivered prefix from fallback payloads.\\n\\nFixes #58601\\n\\nthanks @bradgroux\",\n      \"tree\": {\n        \"sha\": \"b55956097568c1f4f4a79421214a4e227363c237\",\n        \"url\": \"https://api.github.com/repos/openclaw/openclaw/git/trees/b55956097568c1f4f4a79421214a4e227363c237\"\n      },\n      \"url\": \"https://api.github.com/repos/openclaw/openclaw/git/commits/57949397fa181dc56fbfdb86fa1fa292bb25faea\",\n      \"comment_count\": 0,\n      \"verification\": {\n        \"verified\": true,\n        \"reason\": \"valid\",\n        \"signature\": \"-----BEGIN PGP SIGNATURE-----\\n\\nwsFcBAABCAAQBQJpzbJHCRC1aQ7uu5UhlAAAfbsQAC8xWizMy1DD2YZON+dhRtio\\n0F7/BxzZUGZup3eGAg5MnSwxozVhc/2JzKN3OjfGsx40j3jDwDsKYKpxFSxS93Ge\\n5eb84B9qYEdyKJxlBz2aybX6KdKawxTPbE+VREZw6fS0gdKAQumMU31hOLgTD4Cm\\n0dFC3TMS/lfRfBAf+hXwM118RXdIGZ4hb8353TbDk2aaQFbcrPHiG68CvXgjPbDZ\\nt3RKKPUYklM5vJfdNkja1yxhX2njxAKSm+c5Zhmz4+Irf7QURCFFgHzELMxus3cd\\nNk8mNqg3cn20ALMxmTFRCjqe1Eks0/VKH4bOIlYkg9KEZvQq7mFwW72eVHTU5/1q\\n72cpuSw//i/cfi3D7TIXK6AIra+d5qNUT2PVPNLpErTyh572iulvsxMGv+7UP2hY\\nM3TzY98atxAltuV8qlTQhES53tmnjYJ4UFpQTX5rCN6HAZYE/SppEgMh6JTJSS6g\\nQMCcm+DQ5HBnjUsgiAq4gelWxooY5lX88iV1f0JWN5lh6kUPm1jK7MWmfwudaPVG\\n0NlQjjeVnwqN6T3eA7Cz1GbypD9jKkLunSx6E6OeLlI9kIN2NZC6L0g6FyPpyQBz\\n4ayAMTZJkHeqfmtsNgVbanTcjznQrcXIcOLvugU9jRVV5OGUSBS6oWrqPpAeQlLK\\nyx2qi2oN6gvF9kot+KYU\\n=ygbb\\n-----END PGP SIGNATURE-----\\n\",\n        \"payload\": \"tree b55956097568c1f4f4a79421214a4e227363c237\\nparent 560ea25294686456ca5c28fd53736bdb61b23b91\\nauthor Brad Groux <3053586+BradGroux@users.noreply.github.com> 1775088199 -0500\\ncommitter GitHub <noreply@github.com> 1775088199 -0500\\n\\nfix(msteams): prevent duplicate text when stream exceeds 4000 char limit (#59297)\\n\\nWhen a streamed response exceeds TEAMS_MAX_CHARS, the stream sets streamFailed=true and finalizes. Previously, hasContent returned false when streamFailed was true, causing preparePayload to pass through the full payload for block delivery, duplicating already-streamed text.\\n\\nNow tracks streamed length and strips the already-delivered prefix from fallback payloads.\\n\\nFixes #58601\\n\\nthanks @bradgroux\",\n        \"verified_at\": \"2026-04-02T00:03:20Z\"\n      }\n    },\n    \"url\": \"https://api.github.com/repos/openclaw/openclaw/commits/57949397fa181dc56fbfdb86fa1fa292bb25faea\",\n    \"html_url\": \"https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/commit/57949397fa181dc56fbfdb86fa1fa292bb25faea\",\n    \"comments_url\": \"https://api.github.com/repos/openclaw/openclaw/commits/57949397fa181dc56fbfdb86fa1fa292bb25faea/comments\",\n    \"author\": {\n      \"login\": \"BradGroux\",\n      \"id\": 3053586,\n      \"node_id\": \"MDQ6VXNlcjMwNTM1ODY=\",\n      \"avatar_url\": \"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/3053586?v=4\",\n      \"gravatar_id\": \"\",\n      \"url\": \"https://api.github.com/users/BradGroux\",\n      \"html_url\": \"https://github.com/BradGroux\",\n      \"followers_url\": \"https://api.github.com/users/BradGroux/followers\",\n      \"following_url\": \"https://api.github.com/users/BradGroux/following{/other_user}\",\n      \"gists_url\": \"https://api.github.com/users/BradGroux/gists{/gist_id}\",\n      \"starred_url\": \"https://api.github.com/users/BradGroux/starred{/owner}{/repo}\",\n      \"subscriptions_url\": \"https://api.github.com/users/BradGroux/subscriptions\",\n      \"organizations_url\": \"https://api.github.com/users/BradGroux/org