{"type":"compaction","id":"b32a95d1","parentId":"812058f4","timestamp":"2026-04-02T00:30:58.447Z","summary":"## Decisions\nNo prior history.\n\n## Open TODOs\nNone.\n\n## Constraints/Rules\nNone.\n\n## Pending user asks\nNone.\n\n## Exact identifiers\nNone captured.\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n## Decisions\n- **Fallback to GitHub API after failed web searches**: Web search via Kimi API failed twice with 401 authentication errors, so switched to fetching OpenClaw updates via GitHub\n- No new decisions have been made in the latest update\n\n## Open TODOs\n- Complete the pending daily task `openclaw_daily_news`: search latest OpenClaw资讯, filter 2-3 valuable updates, write a 800-1500 word WeChat Official Account article, save to `wechat_articles/openclaw_YYYYMMDD.md`\n- Obtain recent OpenClaw commit and release data from GitHub API\n\n## Constraints/Rules\n- Read HEARTBEAT.md from exact path `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md`, do not read `docs/heartbeat.md`\n- Follow HEARTBEAT.md strictly, do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats\n- Article requirements: tone is professional but not boring, audience is technical/developer, length 800-1500 words, structure includes attractive title, lead/summary, body content, closing summary\n\n## Pending user asks\n- Process the pending daily task `openclaw_daily_news` found in the workspace tasks directory\n\n## Exact identifiers\n- Exact HEARTBEAT path: `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md`\n- Pending task file: `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/tasks/openclaw_daily_20260402.json`\n- Current time: 2026-04-02 08:08 AM (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-04-02 00:08 UTC\n- Task ID: `openclaw_daily_news`\n- Session ID: `neat-river`\n- PID: 23663\n- Web search error: `Kimi API error (401): {\"error\":{\"message\":\"Invalid Authentication\",\"type\":\"invalid_authentication_error\"}}`\n- GitHub repo URL: `https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw`\n- GitHub API URL: `https://api.github.com/repo