{"type":"message","id":"ff3b9591","parentId":"b32a95d1","timestamp":"2026-04-02T00:30:58.489Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-02 08:30:00 GMT+8] 🔔 每日定时任务：检查并执行 OpenClaw 每日资讯推送任务\nSystem: \nSystem: 请执行以下步骤：\nSystem: 1. 检查 /Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/tasks/ 目录下是否有今天的 pending 任务 openclaw_daily_YYYYMMDD.json\nSystem: 2. 如果有任务，按照任务 instructions 和 steps 执行：搜索 OpenClaw 最新资讯，生成微信公众号文章，保存到 wechat_articles/ 目录\nSystem: 3. 完成后将文章发送到钉钉群 cidUNAfzlz+0GntERJWlrGXIw==\nSystem: 4. 更新任务状态为 completed\n\nA scheduled reminder has been triggered. The reminder content is:\n\n🔔 每日定时任务：检查并执行 OpenClaw 每日资讯推送任务\n\n请执行以下步骤：\n1. 检查 /Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/tasks/ 目录下是否有今天的 pending 任务 openclaw_daily_YYYYMMDD.json\n2. 如果有任务，按照任务 instructions 和 steps 执行：搜索 OpenClaw 最新资讯，生成微信公众号文章，保存到 wechat_articles/ 目录\n3. 完成后将文章发送到钉钉群 cidUNAfzlz+0GntERJWlrGXIw==\n4. 更新任务状态为 completed\n\nHandle this reminder internally. Do not relay it to the user unless explicitly requested.\nCurrent time: Thursday, April 2nd, 2026 — 8:30 AM (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-04-02 00:30 UTC"}],"timestamp":1775089858448}}
